original: Yllner, Nils Gustaf Natanael, tandläkare, Norrköping, f. 16/8/95 i Höja, Kristianst. 1., av kontr :prosten Axel Y. o. Ida Trägårdh. G. 21 m. Tyra Lind. Barn: Rolf f. 22, odont. kand., Ingegerd 26, Birgitta 32. — Stud:ex. v. Östra real i Sthlm 15, ing:ex. i Stre-litz 20, tandhkand. 25, tandläk. 27. Praktik i Norrköp. sed. 27. Ordf. i Odont. fören. 26-27.
translated: Yllner, Nils Gustaf Natanael, dentist, Norrköping, b. August 16th, 1895 in Höja, Kristianstad county, son of the dean Axel Y. and Ida Trägårdh. Married in 1921 to Tyra Lind. Children: Rolf b. 1922, dental student, Ingegerd b. 1926, Birgitta b. 1932. Completed secondary school at Östra Real in Stockholm in 1915, graduated with an engineering degree in Stre-litz in 1920, obtained a dental degree in 1925, became a licensed dentist in 1927. Practiced dentistry in Norrköping since 1927. Served as chairman of the Odontological Society in 1926-1927.
